snippet.title: Battlefield 10th Anniversary: Battlefield Vietnam (2004)
snippet.description:
Celebrating 10 years of Battlefield, this is one of the classic trailers produced for Battlefield Vietnam.

Read our retrospective of Battlefield Vietnam at the Battlefield Blog: http://bit.ly/Q057ca

Stay tuned as we continue the Battlefield 10 year anniversary with more retrospectives, classic trailers, developer interviews, and reveals of old school concept art.
